    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArchiveDecorator, IndexDirectoryDecorator
    public abstract class DirectoryDecorator<W extends Writable<W>>
extends Object
implements Directory<W>
    Decorates a Directory (e.g. to modify its files, subdirectories, etc.) on Writable.prepare(app.coronawarn.server.services.distribution.assembly.structure.util.ImmutableStack<java.lang.Object>). This class proxies all function calls to the Directory it decorates.
